channel.title: The Insigniat Project!
channel.description:
Hello players! This is the owner of the Insigniat Project here, and I would like to welcome you too my server! It is a pking only server but it is also an economy server! so you can't spawn item's but you can obtain new items by killing players and earning pkp's, and using them in the pkp shop! :) Also there are a few ways too make money if you ever run low! Like thieving, killing frost dragons, killing bork, and killing ice strykewyrms!! :) Join and kill them too find out there special drops! (;
Pictures will be posted soon along with some promotional video's of the server!
Please and thank you and safe regards from - Insigniat
https://dl.dropbox.com/u/94814358/Insigniat%20Client%20v2.zip
http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?lg2366w361l6su6
New client with new models and other items added into the game! Take the cache provided in the folder and replace it with your old one! :) Please and thank you!
If you don't know where to place the cache then put it in your C:\users\bill (just an example) and if you still don't know how to do it message me on the forums and I will help
~Insigniat
